title: Best of Manomay Bhattacharya Songs | Top Bengali Songs Jukebox
description:
This Jukebox presents 10 selected Bengali modern version songs rendered by MANOMAY BHATTACHARYA who is  an well known contemporary artist of West Bengal. These songs were written by Suvo Dasgupta and set tunes from various popular Hindi Film songs had composed by great music directors like Ravi, Shankar Jaikrishan, O P Nayyar, Madan Mohan & Kalyanji Anandji. These version songs of Manomay has been recorded & released in 1999 from Saregama as a PUJA album "GAAN-I AMAR PRAN". Hope you will enjoy these Bengali modern songs set on evergreen Hindi film tunes.
